high_descs: Turn right and head towards the box on the countertop  on your right.

Place the cup in the fridge and pick it back after few seconds.
Turn around to the cabinet below the counter to your left.
Place the cup in the cabinet by opening it, then close it.

high_descs: Turn right and go across to the counter top on the right.

Place the cup in the fridge on the bottom shelf, close the fridge, then take the cup out of the fridge.
Turn to the cabinet below the counter top and cardboard box.
Place the cup in the cabinet to the right side.
anns.task_desc: Place a cool cup in the cabinet.
